---
import "../../../styles/home/home.css";
---

<div class="service-row reverse section">
  <div class="service-text">
    <span class="service-tag">For Unique Businesses</span>
    <h3>Custom WordPress Development</h3>
    <p>
      If your business has unique data (like Listings, Rentals, or Directories),
      standard themes won't work. I build a custom dashboard using ACF so you
      can easily input data without breaking the design.
    </p>
    <div class="best-for-box">
      <strong>Best for:</strong>
      <ul>
        <li>Real Estate Agencies</li>
        <li>Directory Websites</li>
        <li>Custom Brand Designs</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="service-image">
    <img
      src="/assets/Icons/online-resume-and-portfolio-website-design-wordpress.png"
      alt="Custom WP"
    />
  </div>
</div>
